  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will examine outcomes for patients treated by planned culotte stenting and compare
      outcomes with 2 different stent platforms, the next generation Synergy II and the Xience
      Xpedition DES platforms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
